edu.columbia.stat.wood.sequencememoizer
Class Sequence

java.lang.Object
  edu.columbia.stat.wood.sequencememoizer.Sequence

public class Sequence
extends java.lang.Object

Container object for an int[] containing the values of the sequence being memoized. Object implements specific methods useful in the data manipulation needed for the sequence memoizer.

Author:
nicholasbartlett
